Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:16.04,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}奉獻給你
